{"ts":"2026-06-26T22:01:07.290Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Designing Customer Resolution**\n\nI'm currently designing an automated customer resolution agent. I've defined the platform as a Hybrid Cloud, with stages including an Omnichannel Hook, Intent Classifier, Knowledge Fetch, and Human Gate Route. The system will leverage Zendesk Webhooks, Salesforce CRM, and Braze Messaging Hub as data sources. My goal is an 84.5% automated resolution rate, based on a strict return policy. I've designed a sandbox response to test the process and human gateway requirement.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T22:01:08.705Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Constructing Liquidity Projections**\n\nI'm working on a system to simulate market variance projections, with a focus on liquidity ratios and capital reserves, for board-level decision reports. Currently, I'm integrating data from Snowflake, general ledgers, and macro feeds. The system is built with a risk modeler engine, summarizer node, and sovereign PDF compile stage. The target is a 99.5% trend projection matching rate. My primary use case is cross-industry executive strategy.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
