d and resolved. I am verifying the \"100% Rate Error Identification Rate\" against the system prompt's instructions for bills of lading discrepancies, particularly concerning discrepancies exceeding $10. The sandbox response indicates promising results in auditing invoices and cross-referencing rates against tariffs.\n\n\n"}}
